{"tid":1540471,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 民陣宣佈9.8搞促請美國政府通過人權法大遊行！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:36:57.000Z","uid":167548,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0282071056a3706480f6161b7d1c24eef96a31","tid":1540471,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住做左標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <br />\n但是9.8真是好關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">同我推到民陣搞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>9.8 贏到開巷, 放下成見！<br />\n雙劍合壁 民陣遊行+連登集會！<br />\n民陣：維園到美領附近<br />\n連登：美領集會！</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次再強調全面和平理性非暴力, 向美國喊苦喊忽晒馬唱國歌拎民意比國會議員去繼續推人權法！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：不反對通知書都唔批啦有鬼用？</span><br />\nA：其實呢個是<span style=\"color: gold;\">seek緊attention</span>, 你唔申請搵鬼知咩！唔批佢先會幫手唱鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋講明和理非去美領叫冤啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />離開同溫層是沒人知9.8有遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：申請完又ban 直接去就得了</span><br />\nA：佢Ban還Ban, 但是你要全部媒體幫手報得民陣做到。你睇下除左連登是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無媒體幫手報</span></strong></span>, 蘋果都沒啊, 醒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n民陣！<br />\n快申請不反對通知書！<br />\n9.8 通過人權法大遊行去美領！<br />\n用民陣知名度幫手路過美領！<br />\n去刷爆我地連登流水式集會！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f463876a24602316cea844f39a90c83b6ccf7e4","tid":1540471,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,